%N A397843 Numbers k such that sigma(k) = psi(k) + Omega(k)^4.
%e A397843 868 is a term since sigma(868) = 1792 = 1536 + 4^4 = psi(868) + Omega(868)^4.
%o A397843 (PARI) isok(k) = {my(f = factor(k)); sigma(f) == prod(i=1, #f~, (f[i, 1]+1) * f[i, 1]^(f[i, 2]-1)) + bigomega(f)^4; } \\ _Amiram Eldar_, Jul 12 2026
